od lessons=E2=80=9D (https://www.brainpickings.org/2015/06/11/the-spiritua=
l-uses-of-fruit-trees-ralph-austen/?mc_cid=3D1ffb15db80&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]=
) and Hermann Hesse called them =E2=80=9Cthe most penetrating of preachers=
=2E=E2=80=9D (https://www.brainpickings.org/2012/09/21/hermann-hesse-trees/?=
mc_cid=3D1ffb15db80&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID])

http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1592701914/braipick-20?mc_cid=3D1ff=
b15db80&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]

It is both a pity and a strange comfort that Sanna=E2=80=99s luminous=2C b=
uoyant watercolors and his masterful subtlety of scale don=E2=80=99t fully=
