30/pablo-neruda-childhood-and-poetry/?mc_cid=3D1ffb15db80&mc_eid=3D[UNIQI=
D]) =2C Joan Didion (https://www.brainpickings.org/2012/10/16/why-i-write-=
joan-didion/?mc_cid=3D1ffb15db80&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) =2C David Foster Wall=
